  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Chad Second Programmatic Economic Recovery and Resilience Grant</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The development objectives and pillars of Second Programmatic Economic Recovery and Resilience Development Policy Financing Project are to (1) enhance fiscal risk management; (2) improve oil revenue transparency and management; (3) promote resilience and economic diversification in key real sectors; and (4) increase social protection for the poor and vulnerable. This operation is the second in a programmatic series of two development policy grants for the period 2017-2020, and is well aligned with the strategic objectives of the 2017-2021 national development plan (NDP).</narrative>
  </description>
